Detailed Description

template<class MapType>
class tLoadingSystem< MapType >

File: loadtemplate.h

Description: Template for loading systems

(c)2009, by Raymond Loeberg Template for a loading system. Contains functions to store, get, and retrieve instances. All instances are stored in a private map.
